1364
01:43:02,390 --> 01:43:04,560
I don't deserve you.

1365
01:43:05,040 --> 01:43:06,870
I'm a liar.

1366
01:43:17,520 --> 01:43:18,240
Forget it.

1367
01:43:18,600 --> 01:43:19,430
Let it go.

1368
01:43:27,640 --> 01:43:28,680
Maybe

1369
